    description: "Nginx server block as raw string configuration."
    shapeIndex: 4
    mamlText: "# Nginx configuration\n{\n  name: \"diligent-translation.info\"\n  # Server block\n  config: \"\"\"\nserver {\n    listen 443 ssl http2;\n    server_name vengeful-disposer.name;\n\n    ssl_certificate /etc/ssl/certs/cert.pem;\n    ssl_certificate_key /etc/ssl/private/key.pem;\n\n    location / {\n        proxy_pass http://localhost:3707;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;\n    }\n\n    location /static/ {\n        root /var/www/html;\n        expires 30d;\n    }\n}\n\"\"\"\n\n  enabled: true\n  reload_command: \"nginx -t && systemctl reload nginx\"\n}"
  }
